## Skills — `/skills/`

Read-only capability packs containing playbooks and `SKILL.md` files.
The skills middleware auto-matches relevant skills at the start of each run
and injects their metadata into your state; you can then `read_file` the
specific `SKILL.md` for detailed guidance.

- Treat the entire `/skills/` tree as read-only — do NOT `edit_file` or
  `write_file` under `/skills/**`.  Skill authoring happens outside the
  agent loop.
- Prefer matched skills over improvising your own methodology.  If the
  matched skill set is empty or doesn't fit, fall back to general
  reasoning and note the gap.
